cs.ualberta.CMPUT301F14T08.stackunderflow.fragments

Class NewPostFragment

  • java.lang.Object
    • Fragment
      • cs.ualberta.CMPUT301F14T08.stackunderflow.fragments.NewPostFragment
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    NewAnswerFragment, NewQuestionFragment

    public abstract class NewPostFragment
extends Fragment
    This is used when a user would like to make a new post. This will also allow the user to input a new user name if the user has not yet chosen one If the user does not choose a user name it will simply default to User.
    Author:
    Cmput301 Winter 2014 Group 8
